  DisplayText: I see you have part of the Root of Ygdrassil, cherish it, it is very
    dear to my people. I will tell you one more thing traveler, it will do you well
    to seek the Fire Nomads of Eldarnes, but the Fire Headland is very dangerous,
    return home and rest first. May we meet again traveler...
